-- NHPC Said to Plan Raising 15 Billion Rupees From Bond Sale
-- B y   K a r t i k a y   M e h r o t r a
-- 2012-02-24T10:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-24/nhpc-said-to-plan-raising-15-billion-rupees-from-bond-sale.html
NHPC Ltd. (NHPC) , an Indian hydroelectric
power producer, plans to raise as much as 15 billion rupees
($305 million) selling 15-year bonds, according to a person with
direct knowledge of the matter.  The company will open a book-building auction on March 5 to
sell the bonds, the person said, asking not to be identified as
the matter is private. The auction closes on March 6, the person
said.  NHPC Executive Director R.K. Taneja was not available for
comment when called at his office phone number in  New Delhi .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kartikay Mehrotra in New Delhi at 
 kmehrotra2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
